Format of the files .dat: a sequence of wims records, like
this example:

:Fe + H^+ -> Fe^2+ + H2,2,2, Fe , 2H^+ , Fe^{2+} , H2,1,2,1,1,55.8

The list contains
*  one non-equilibrated equation of reaction (Fe + H^+ -> Fe^2+ + H2)
* the number of terms in the left member of the reaction (2)
* the number of terms in the right member of the reaction (2)
* first chemical species with stœchiometric coeff. (Fe)
* second chemical species with stœchiometric coeff. (2H^+)
* ... (Fe^{2+} , H2)
* list of the stœchiometric coeffs (1,2,1,1)
* molar mass of the first component (55.8)
